# Invoice Generator — Project Blueprint

## Project Overview

A modern, feature-rich invoice generation web app that **surpasses invoice-generator.com** in design, UX, and functionality. The platform monetizes through:
- **Ad-supported free tier** (sidebar + banner ads)
- **Paid subscription (Pro)** — ad-free, unlocks premium features

---

## Tech Stack

| Layer | Technology |
|-------|-----------|
| Frontend | React + Vite (or Next.js for SSR/SEO) |
| Styling | Tailwind CSS + shadcn/ui |
| State | Zustand or React Context |
| PDF Generation | `@react-pdf/renderer` or `jsPDF` + `html2canvas` |
| Auth | Clerk or Supabase Auth |
| Backend/DB | Supabase (Postgres + Storage) |
| Payments | Stripe |
| Ads | Google AdSense |
| Hosting | Vercel or Netlify |

