## Core Features (Free Tier)

### Invoice Builder
- [x] Live real-time preview (split-pane: editor left, preview right)
- [x] Add/remove/reorder line items (drag-and-drop)
- [x] Custom fields (quantity, rate, description, tax per item)
- [x] Multiple tax support (GST, VAT, HST, custom %)
- [x] Discount support (flat or percentage)
- [x] Shipping fee field
- [x] Currency selector (150+ currencies with symbols)
- [x] Auto-calculated subtotal, tax, discount, total
- [x] Invoice number with auto-increment
- [x] Issue date & due date pickers
- [x] Payment terms dropdown (Net 7, Net 30, Due on Receipt, custom)
- [x] Notes / Terms & Conditions field
- [x] Upload company logo
- [x] From / Bill To / Ship To sections
- [x] Download as PDF (free, with subtle watermark or branding)
- [x] Download as PNG
- [x] Print directly
- [x] Share via link (view-only)

### UX Enhancements Over Competitors
- Split-screen live preview (no page reload)
- Autosave to localStorage
- Keyboard shortcuts (⌘+S to save, ⌘+P to print, etc.)
- Undo/redo history
- Mobile-responsive builder
- One-click "Clear All" with confirmation
- Smart client autocomplete (remembers past entries)

