## Monetization Architecture

### Ads (Free Tier)
- **Sidebar ads**: Fixed 300×250 or 160×600 AdSense units
- **Top banner**: 728×90 leaderboard (desktop)
- **Between-section ads**: Native-style inside builder (non-intrusive)
- Lazy-load ads to not hurt performance
- Ad slots clearly separated from UI, never blocking workflow

### Subscriptions (Pro)
- Stripe Checkout for payment
- Stripe Customer Portal for billing management
- Webhook-driven entitlement in Supabase
- 7-day free trial on Pro

---

## Design Direction

**Aesthetic:** Clean, modern SaaS — think Notion × Linear × Stripe
- **Primary font:** `DM Sans` (headings) + `Inter` (body)
- **Color palette:** Deep navy `#0F172A` accents with electric blue `#3B82F6` CTA, white backgrounds
- **Layout:** 60/40 split-pane builder on desktop, stacked on mobile
- **Micro-interactions:** Smooth field focus transitions, line item fade-in, PDF preview slide-in
- **Dark mode:** Full support via Tailwind `dark:` classes

