## Database Schema (Supabase)

```sql
-- Users (via Supabase Auth)
profiles (id, email, name, plan, stripe_customer_id, created_at)

-- Invoices
invoices (id, user_id, invoice_number, status, data jsonb, template, created_at, updated_at)

-- Clients
clients (id, user_id, name, email, address, phone, notes)

-- Subscriptions
subscriptions (id, user_id, stripe_subscription_id, plan, status, current_period_end)
```

